title: Fans Choice winner & Sports OT Preview
text:
Fans Choice winner & Sports OT Preview Posted: Updated: 
CENTRAL LAKE – Central Lake welcomes in Ski Valley Conference foe Mancelona Friday night as our “Fans’ Choice Game of the Week,” leading off the Double Overtime portion our Sports Overtime. 
For our “Overtime on the Road” matchup, Charlevoix (5-2, 3-0 NMFL) hosts No. 10 Frankfort (6-1, 4-0 NMFL) for the Northern Michigan Football League Legends Division championship. 
"We basically have our own destiny to take care of, because we have to win Friday night, and then we have to turn around again and go up against a much-improved Harbor Springs team on the following Friday at their place,” Charlevoix coach Ron Bindi said. 
We'll have a live preview from Charlevoix on Friday's 9&10 News at 6 p.m. 
These are just two of the 18 local football games and one college hockey game that we plan to show Friday night on Sports Overtime. SHANNON McGRATTAN
